| What changed | Why it matters |
|---|---|
| `injectStyles()` is idempotent (checks ID first) | Prevents duplicate `<style>` tags on SPA re-runs |
| All CSS scoped under `.sightseeing-carousel` | Won't bleed into or conflict with host page styles |
| `rel="noopener noreferrer"` on links | Prevents tab-napping security vulnerability |
| `img.alt` set from `overlayLabels` | Accessibility + SEO compliance |
| `img.loading = 'lazy'` | Faster page load, especially with 16 images |
| `leftArrow.disabled` / `rightArrow.disabled` | Prevents double-clicks firing scroll past bounds |
| `scroll` event listener on `trackWrapper` | Arrow states update correctly on touch/swipe too |
| `CARD_WIDTH` corrected to `170 + 15` | Was using `282` (wrong), causing over-scroll on click |
| Stale carousel detection on SPA re-mount | Removes ghost node before re-inserting |
| `history.pushState` safely bound before override | Avoids breaking the original function reference |
